OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776764340
OL,3,CFinal designs revealed for Queen
OL,4,CElizabeth II memorial statue
OL,6,FA bronze statue of the Queen in her
OL,7,F20s will stand overlooking The Mall,
OL,8,Fat the entrance to the St James's Park
OL,9,Fmemorial, designed by renowned
OL,10,Farchitect Lord Foster, and inspired by
OL,11,Fa famous portrait.
OL,13,FIt will feature a family of gardens
OL,14,Fthrough the park with meandering paths
OL,15,Fand a new translucent, glass unity
OL,16,Fbridge - likely to be called the Queen
OL,17,FElizabeth Bridge - inspired by the
OL,18,Flate Queen's wedding tiara and
OL,19,Freplacing the current Blue Bridge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
