PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776764340
OL,3,CFinal designs revealed for Queen
OL,4,CElizabeth II memorial statue
OL,6,FA smaller statue of her consort,
OL,7,FPrince Philip, the late Duke of
OL,8,FEdinburgh, in his Naval uniform, will
OL,9,Fbe a "few paces behind" the Queen,
OL,10,Flooking up at his wife of more than 70
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FThe likeness of the Queen by sculptor
OL,14,FMartin Jennings will take inspiration
OL,15,Ffrom the celebrated 1955 portrait of
OL,16,FElizabeth II by Italian artist Pietro
OL,17,FAnnigoni.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
