PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776764340
OL,3,CFinal designs revealed for Queen
OL,4,CElizabeth II memorial statue
OL,6,FThe Queen sat for Annigoni at
OL,7,FBuckingham Palace in late 1954 when
OL,8,Fshe was just 28 and the Renaissance-
OL,9,Fstyle painting was completed the
OL,10,Ffollowing year.
OL,12,FThe statue will stand 7.3 metres high
OL,13,F- with the Queen three metres tall on
OL,14,Fa 4.3-metre plinth ` in a new civic
OL,15,Fspace called Queen Elizabeth II Place
OL,16,Fat Marlborough Gate on the edge of the
OL,17,Fpark.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
