PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776764340
OL,3,CFinal designs revealed for Queen
OL,4,CElizabeth II memorial statue
OL,6,FThe smaller companion statue ` 3.8
OL,7,Fmetres in height with a 2.3-metre
OL,8,Ffigure and a 1.5-metre plinth, of the
OL,9,Fduke, will be located 20 metres behind
OL,10,Fin the park.
OL,12,FPhilip will be represented at a
OL,13,Fsimilar age, wearing his Admiral-of-
OL,14,Fthe-Fleet uniform.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
