CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776764340
OL,3,CFinal designs revealed for Queen
OL,4,CElizabeth II memorial statue
OL,6,FThe King, Queen Camilla and other
OL,7,Fmembers of the royal family will view
OL,8,Fmaquettes of the planned statues and a
OL,9,Fscale model of the wider memorial when
OL,10,Fthey visit the British Museum on
OL,11,FTuesday, as part of events
OL,12,Fcommemorating what would have been the
OL,13,FQueen's centenary.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
