OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776764340
OL,3,CFinal designs revealed for Queen
OL,4,CElizabeth II memorial statue
OL,6,FLord Janvrin said the Annigoni
OL,7,Fportrait was a "lovely, iconic image
OL,8,Fof the young Queen."
OL,10,FHe added: "We think probably most
OL,11,Fpeople would like to be remembered
OL,12,Fwhen they were young.
OL,14,F"But at the Birdcage Walk end, we will
OL,15,Fhave a bust of the Queen in what I
OL,16,Fcall her later years, not very old,
OL,17,Fbut probably when she was in her
OL,18,Ffifties, sixties."
OL,26,@oD@POUpD@TO]rD@KOUvD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
