PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776764340
OL,3,CFinal designs revealed for Queen
OL,4,CElizabeth II memorial statue
OL,6,FThe bust of the more mature Queen will
OL,7,Fbe crafted by artist Karen Newman for
OL,8,Fthe other side of the park.
OL,10,FThe memorial is expected to be
OL,11,Fcompleted in 2028.
OL,13,FIt is one of three projects underway
OL,14,Fin honour of the Queen, with a new
OL,15,Fcharity, The Queen Elizabeth Trust,
OL,16,Fand a Digital Memorial also launched
OL,17,Fon Tuesday.
OL,19,FThe Digital Memorial aims to create a
OL,20,F"living archive" made of the public's
OL,21,Fpersonal memories of the Queen.
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
