OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776764340
OL,3,CFinal designs revealed for Queen
OL,4,CElizabeth II memorial statue
OL,6,FIt will digitise the Court Circular `
OL,7,Fthe daily record of official royal
OL,8,Fengagements ` and bring it to life,
OL,9,Fmapping key events from the Queen's
OL,10,Freign.
OL,12,FThe public will be asked to contribute
OL,13,Ftheir recollections via the website
OL,14,FQueenelizabeth.com ` which was
OL,15,Fpreviously owned by the luxury cruise
OL,16,Fline Cunard for the Queen Elizabeth
OL,17,Fship, but was donated by the company
OL,18,Fafter a request from the digital
OL,19,Fmemorial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
