OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776764340
OL,3,CFinal designs revealed for Queen
OL,4,CElizabeth II memorial statue
OL,6,FJoe Garner, the Queen Elizabeth
OL,7,FMemorial Committee member who
OL,8,Fspecialised on the digital memorial,
OL,9,Fsaid: "We could create the most
OL,10,Fphenomenal archive."
OL,12,FHe suggested it could develop into
OL,13,Fadding cinefilm and photos from the
OL,14,Fpublic, and would be expanded to map
OL,15,Fmemories from around the globe.
OL,17,FRecorded footage of memories from
OL,18,Fcelebrities, including Olympian Tom
OL,19,FDaley and artist Dame Tracey Emin,
OL,20,Falready features on the new site.
OL,26,@qD@GOUrD@TO]
